{"tid":2211692,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蘇文隆: 鐵鎚在身推論必然意圖破壞公物 青年罪成還柙候判","createTime":"2020-09-21T09:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T13:22:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"ecb7d685f5c24542cfb2bcf93414b072daee8994","tid":2211692,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"蘇官指，眾所周知，香港在事發前數月出現警民衝突，有示威者用鐵鎚敲毁交通燈及燈箱等公物，示威者亦戴上面罩及護目鏡等物以保密身份，認為被告管有兩支鐵鎚實有非法用途，即破壞公物，更指這是唯一及必然的推論，裁定被告罪成。不過，對於被告藏有的登山杖及摺刀，蘇官裁定兩者均沒有非法用途。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情稱，被告去年大學畢業後任職市場營銷工作，但環境轉差，現從事兼職工作。被告親撰求情信則稱，定罪對他的前途影響很大，望能輕判。蘇官指案情嚴重，先索取勞教中心報告，並將被告還柙至下月8日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/V3MBSEZBRJGUFGPJVDRX36HMYU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FV3MBSEZBRJGUFGPJVDRX36HMYU%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=0b9d541f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2FV3MBSEZBRJGUFGPJVDRX36HMYU%2F&h=7984b57b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/V3MBSEZBRJGUFGPJVDRX36HMYU/</a>"},{"pid":"34b7022c738ef29f7091c23258845abc505eb91d","tid":2211692,"uid":32691,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"帶刀出黎果幾件呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91758a29d22e92588dae1994a8516e6ee3524cb","tid":2211692,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b7022c738ef29f7091c23258845abc505eb91d","tid":2211692,"uid":32691,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:18.000Z","msg":"帶刀出黎果幾件呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"r