/><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:40:04.000Z","msg":"食生果同斬人都唔犯法,好有俠義骨風,情操高尚!!!"},{"pid":"3fb309ba4d7998f86d8b46b39d052de49b588346","tid":2211692,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c79f4e27e613decec47cb7b0562a8215d623db1","tid":2211692,"uid":188804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"上訴啦<br />\n咁薄弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:40:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b1402ee8853c9f18dfd90e77c1dea27b2c66bbfb","tid":2211692,"uid":5312,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"疑點利益歸於原告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edef72a527f94cb0ba61de5b7f81b336b5e7e29","tid":2211692,"uid":304431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"蘇文隆係咪想強姦小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20915a085c3b39a67e7e40a7d19d4050012f9c7","tid":2211692,"uid":5312,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7c79f4e27e613decec47cb7b0562a8215d623db1","tid":2211692,"uid":188804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:39:24.000Z","msg":"上訴啦<br />\n咁薄弱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:41:57.000Z","msg":"好多單都係官無限FF之後入罪<br />\n又盲目信班所謂警察<br />\n話咩警察唔會咁做，警察唔會咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a8deb2a5057d8dbc508144be6010714384909e","tid":2211692,"uid":51349,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"時天旱禁酒，釀者有刑。<br />\n吏於人家索得釀具，論者欲令與作酒者同罰。<br />\n雍與先主遊觀，見一男女行道，謂先主曰︰<br />\n「彼人欲行淫，何以不縛？」<br />\n先主曰︰<br />\n「卿何以知之？」<br />\n雍對曰︰<br />\n「彼有其具，與欲釀者同。」<br />\n先主大笑，而原欲釀者。<br />\n雍之滑稽，皆此類也。<br />\n<br />\n有一段時日，蜀漢遇上旱災，先主劉備為了避免浪費糧和水，以度過難關起見，而頒下禁止釀酒的特別令來因應。<br />\n不料，官員們卻執行過當，只要在老百姓家中搜出釀酒器具，不管是否正在使用？都一律想當作釀酒現行犯論罪。<br />\n在某日，簡雍與劉備一同出遊時，路上迎面行來一男一女，簡雍突然指著他們對劉備說︰<br />\n「這兩個人想通姦行淫，為什麼不把他們抓起來！」<br />\n劉備聽得莫名其妙，問︰「你是怎麼知道的啊？」<br />\n不料簡雍竟一本正經地說：「他們兩人身上都有&ldquo;犯罪工具&rdquo;，這就跟有了釀酒器具就會想釀酒一樣啊！」<br />\n劉備聽了不禁哈哈大笑，知道自己的政策被執行過了頭，於是便下令釋放了那些想釀酒而擁有器具的人。"},{"pid":"b2062424230f51f795cb9ecd5b2e3949d5995ce0","tid":2211692,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"唔知是咪偏見<br />\n越睇佢個樣越覺樣衰<br />\n成個變態look咁"},{"pid":"dbfbb09595f6c058c7e3792646f9c8e248112f67","tid":2211692,"uid":60307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"佢身上有強姦工具 係咪可以入埋佢老強"},{"pid":"72b41d6117a9748fa8910bbb3a9c462e5576bfd8","tid":2211692,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:22.000Z","msg":"未來報告，你班狗官屋企都有菜刀啦，係咪必然意圖斬人呀會？"},{"pid":"a73f4792ca6456af742c0e95a191d1bc87f6bece","tid":2211692,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"蘇文隆啲想像力豐富"},{"pid":"ef7c961d51785cbec3c1b172e6d68e13e44ba6bf","tid":2211692,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=ce54e633\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"d09f8d35b86187edd4ebc5af86df8c34f14d387a","tid":2211692,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef7c961d51785cbec3c1b172e6d68e13e44ba6bf","tid":2211692,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:44:11.000Z","msg":"國際線有任 請每日推Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=ce54e633\" data-auto-link target=